title: Ten Years After - One Of These Days - 8/4/1975 - Winterland (Official)

lastfm.summary: This is classic Alvin Lee. Vocals as imposing as his stage presence. Clean, lightning fast guitar licks and and, for the time, cutting edge effects. Alvin never got the accolades he so richly deserved and joins Johnny Winter as two of the most incredibly underrated guitar/vocalists of all time. Read more on Last.fm.
